<i>Journal of Personal and Ubiquitous Computing</i>,
11(6):465-479,
August,
2007.
Invited paper; special issue of papers from LoCA 2005.
DOI <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s00779-006-0093-4">10.1007/s00779-006-0093-4</a>.
(<a href="abstracts/kim-jclassify.html">Abstract</a>)
(<a href="bibtex/kim-jclassify.bib">BibTeX</a>)
[<a target=_top href = "././kim-jclassify.pdf">PDF</a>]
Copyright &#169;&nbsp;2007 by Springer London.
See also <b><a href="#kim:classify-tr">earlier version</a></b>.
</a>
