<h3>
  <a name="wireless-mesh">Wireless mesh networks [2007-08]</a>
</h3>
<p>Wireless <b>mesh networks</b> provide Wi-Fi service to mobile clients,
much like an infrastructure wireless network, but the backhaul
connection between access points is itself an ad hoc wireless
network. One large challenge in mesh networks is management.  We
developed the <b>MeshMon</b> system, which can inform a sysadmin about
the health of the mesh network and help diagnose any problems with the
network.
<p>

<em>People:</em> Soumendra Nanda.<br>
<em>Funded by</em> the Department of Justice (BJA) through
       <a href="http://www.ists.dartmouth.edu">ISTS</a>.
</p>

